🗺️ Project Roadmap
This project is a real-time chat application built using React (frontend) and Node.js with Socket.IO (backend).

✅ Phase 1: Project Setup
 Initialize Git repository

 Create frontend with Vite + React

 Create backend with Express + Socket.IO

 Connect frontend and backend via WebSocket

🚧 Phase 2: Basic Chat Features
 User enters name to join chat

 Send and receive real-time messages

 Display message list with sender name

 Auto-scroll to latest message

 Add timestamp to each message

🚧 Phase 3: UI/UX Improvements
 Basic chat layout with CSS or Tailwind

 Responsive design for mobile

 Show active users list

 Different colors for each user’s messages

🚧 Phase 4: Advanced Features
 Private messaging (DMs)

 Emoji picker

 Message reactions

 File/image sharing

 Chat history persistence (DB)

🧪 Phase 5: Deployment & Testing
 Host backend (Render, Railway, or Vercel Functions)

 Host frontend (Vercel, Netlify, etc.)

 Environment variable setup

 Add unit/integration tests

 CI/CD setup (optional)
